to a more formal arrangement to manage the  billion highyield portfolio for credit lyonnais which together with a consortium of other international investors provided the capital for lions investment activities the lion business would ultimately be replaced by ares management ares managementedit main article ares management type public founded   independent website wwwaresmgmtcom ares management founded in  was initially established to manage a  billion market value collateralized debt obligation vehicle ares would grow to manage a family of collateralized loan obligation clo vehicles that would invest in capital marketsbased securities including senior bank loans and highyield and mezzanine debt ares was founded by antony ressler and john h kissick both partners at apollo as well as bennett rosenthal who joined the group from the global leveraged finance group at merrill lynch ares i and ii which were raised were structured as market value clos ares iii though ares x were structured as cash flow clos in  ares completed a spinout from apollo management although technically the founders of ares had completed a spinout with the formation of the firm in  they had maintained a close relationship with apollo over its first five years and operated as the west coast affiliate of apollo shortly thereafter ares completed fundraising for ares corporate opportunities fund a special situations investment fund with 0 million of capital under management in  ares debuted a publicly traded business development company ares capital corporation nasdaqarcc in  ares raised a  billion successor special situations fund ares corporate opportunities fund ii referencesedit  httpiragmcomphoenixzhtmlc0pirolnewsarticleid0  apollo global management form 0q for the quarterly period ended march  0 secgov retrieved june  0   leon d black business week snapshot  mittelman melissa  october 0 apollo to raise new lbo fund as it spends more than ever before bloomberg news bloomberg lp retrieved  novemb