e years and operated as the west coast affiliate of apollo shortly thereafter ares completed fundraising for ares corporate opportunities fund a special situations investment fund with 0 million of capital under management in  ares debuted a publicly traded business development company ares capital corporation nasdaqarcc in  ares raised a  billion successor special situations fund ares corporate opportunities fund ii referencesedit  httpiragmcomphoenixzhtmlc0pirolnewsarticleid0  apollo global management form 0q for the quarterly period ended march  0 secgov retrieved june  0   leon d black business week snapshot  mittelman melissa  october 0 apollo to raise new lbo fund as it spends more than ever before bloomberg news bloomberg lp retrieved  november 0   deal maker’s day tally  billion new york times   drexel divided on settlement new york times december    a b exdrexel executives arrange aid for fruit of the loom august    changes at drexel continue new york times march    drexels uncertain future new york times october    bailing out frances biggest bank new york times january    altman edward i the high yield bond market a decade of assessment comparing  with 0 nyu stern school of business 0  hylton richard d corporate bond defaults up sharply in  new york times january    apollo dissolves vail resorts stake archived 0 at the wayback machine deseret news salt lake city oct    company news walter industries bondholders in accord new york times april    settlement for walter industries and creditors new york times october    eii revamps debt plan to offset offer by icahn new york times may    washington hopes vulture investors will buy bad assets new york times february 0   european group pressing its offer for executive life april    executive life indictments brought wall street journal december   archived september   at the wayback machine  he made real estate a science william l mack w’ wharton school of business alumni magazine spring   area property partners